The MiniCMS is very simple cms writen by PHP & Mysql for generating static HTML pages. The MiniCMS output content is some webpages into articles directory and images into img directory.
Dependency: PHP 5.3, MySQL 5.0, blitz http://alexeyrybak.com/blitz/blitz_ru.html is template engine, Twitter bootstrap and JQuery for uploadin images.

The structure of the database in the file db.sql.